==Usage==
<nowiki>{{LocationFinder}} OR {{LocationFinder|Item Name}}</nowiki>

Item parameter doesn't need to be defined in most cases, as it defaults to page name.

Implemented in [[Module:GameData]], which reads the data page directly. The location links point at the interactive map on the source wiki, which has not been migrated.

===Example===
<nowiki>{{LocationFinder|Bone}}</nowiki>
{{LocationFinder|Bone}}

==Data==
Data is stored on [[Template:LocationFinder/data]].
